{"type":null,"faqId":15374,"title":"MediaPad T1 (S8-70x,S8-701U,S8-701w)_連接WiFi熱點上網，間歇性掉線","answer":"<p> </p>\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">1</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">、首先需要和使用者確認使用環境中是否存在障礙物或是多個熱點，建築物阻隔會大大削弱</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">WiFi</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">熱點的信號強度，</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"> </span></p>\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">導致信號變較差時，直至</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">WiFi</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">網路連接斷開；多個</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">WiFi</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">熱點並存的環境下，存在嚴重的相互干擾現象，影響</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">WiFi</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">鏈</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"> </span></p>\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">接的穩定性。建議使用者靠近熱點或連接到信號強的熱點後，再使用平板；</span></p>\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">2</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">、如果用戶不認可或者不太放心，再告知：華為產品上市之後都會做例行的優化工作，對於榮耀平板這類重點</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\"> </span></p>\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">產品的一些關鍵性能的優化會做的更好，請使用者關注系統軟體</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">OTA</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">升級推送的通知，及時將系統升級到最新版本；</span></p>\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">3</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">、如果用戶仍有疑慮：建議使用者將榮耀平板拿到華為網點檢測是否品質問題；</span></p>\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">4</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'PMingLiU','serif'; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">、針對部分想換機並且符合換機條件的用戶，熱線人員按流程協助處理；</span></p>","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":2,"languageId":201,"languageName":"tr_CN","faqCode":"7656","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1412651310000,"seriesProductName":"S8-701u","visitedTimes":260,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"S8-701u,T1","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}